Description:
You arrive at the ruins of an ancient cathedral, after inspecting it for a while, this seems to be the sacred place where Navalea grew up.

Although the cathedral is practically destroyed, you see a halo of celestial light descending on a small altar that is still standing.
DescriptionAction: The altar bathed in holy light seems the perfect place to purify the cursed badge of Navalea.
